16 toward improved birth and infant health outcomes.
17 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
18 the members of this body recognize March 29 to April 5, 2025, as Georgia
19 Community-Based Doula Week.
